{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be user-friendly and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #a00000; /* Deep Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e0b0b0; /* Lighter Red/Pink */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        #games .game-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-item {\n            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .game-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(160,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .game-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .game-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .game-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .game-info .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes button to the bottom */\n        }\n\n        .game-info .btn:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        #about, #contact {\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 15px;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact input,\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        #contact input::placeholder,\n        #contact textarea::placeholder {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            width: auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple animation for emphasis */\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.03); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        .animated-title {\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1 class=\"animated-title\">Crimson Studios</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#games\">Games</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"games\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Latest Titles</h2>\n        <div class=\"game-list\">\n            <div class=\"game-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/a00000/ffffff?text=Game+1+Image\" alt=\"Game 1 Thumbnail\">\n                <div class=\"game-info\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Fury</h3>\n                    <p>An action-packed RPG set in a world of ancient magic and intense combat. Master unique abilities and forge your destiny.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/a00000/ffffff?text=Game+2+Image\" alt=\"Game 2 Thumbnail\">\n                <div class=\"game-info\">\n                    <h3>Shadows of Crimson</h3>\n                    <p>A gripping narrative-driven adventure where every choice matters. Unravel mysteries and survive in a world shrouded in darkness.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/a00000/ffffff?text=Game+3+Image\" alt=\"Game 3 Thumbnail\">\n                <div class=\"game-info\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Velocity</h3>\n                    <p>Experience high-octane racing with futuristic vehicles. Compete on stunning tracks and dominate the competition.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>Crimson Studios is a passionate team of developers dedicated to creating immersive and unforgettable gaming experiences. We believe in pushing the boundaries of interactive entertainment, crafting worlds that players will love to explore and stories that will stay with them long after they put down the controller.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n        <form id=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will get back to you soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}